This project is intended to teach the average user in-depth details about pepper varieties, recipes, and their histories.
This was pretty much a passion project of mine for fun because I had a hyperfixation on peppers. This website was discontinued 
for a year until I decided to bring it back.

Goals for this project...
- Ship it as my first personal project of HackClub to be completed.
- Add a few recipes to "spice" up the site!
- Pique the interest of each user on the website to get them excited about peppers like I was, since I ended up watching 
every pepper YouTube video and we need a bigger community.

Features...
- A descriptive, thoroughly-researched page for each species of pepper.
- A few recipes for the average at-home chef.
- Gardening guides for other users.
- YouTube videos on pages to make it more interactive